        "subject": "LU-6414 lfsck: misc patch to avoid unexpected repairing",
        "message": "LU-6414 lfsck: misc patch to avoid unexpected repairing\n\nIt back port the patch http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/14332/\nand the patch http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/14189/ to b2_7\nto fix the following:\n\n1) Generate D_LFSCK debug log only when the inconsistency needs\n   to be repaired (or failed to be repaired).\n\n2) If the OST-object's PFID EA has not been initialized, then\n   not handle it as inconsistency.\n\n3) verify index before locating target descriptor.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie9e081f1b16c56889dfd281cbbaad3a40bebb0c2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_7"
    }
